Do you want to discover new walks but specifically adapted to dogs?

The idea of ​​Play Dogs is to help and inform dog owners in various ways.

Thanks to Play-Dogs you can easily find:
- New walks, parks, beaches or dog wash for your dog
- Dog related events not far from your home
- Groups of walks to spend and socialize your dog
- Promotions on services and products related to dogs
